description:
The Info Dump is a stream of consciousness podcast hosted by the artist, professor, and living shit post Metis Christodoulou (she/they). These directionless field recordings explore a breadth of topics ranging from game design to avant-garde fashion to the many little OCD demons that live in Metis's brain. She also smokes a lot of weed while recording and is a crazy hot trans girl (づ ￣ ³￣)づ

